[Zechariah 1:18](../../../bib/kjv/zac001.htm#018.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_018">zac 1:18</span></span>

horn

A "horn" is the symbol of a Gentile king ([Dan
7:24](../../../bib/kjv/dan007.htm#024).md); ([Rev
17:12](../../../bib/kjv/rev017.htm#012).md) and the vision is of the four
world empires; ([Dan 2:36-44](../../../bib/kjv/dan002.htm#036).md); ([Dan
7:3-7](../../../bib/kjv/dan007.htm#003).md) which have "scattered Judah,
Israel, and Jerusalem" ([Zac 1:19](../../../bib/kjv/zac001.htm#019).md).

